            <p>The original collection was donated in 2005 and was comprised of ephemera and photographs related to the Allen family and Frank Sullivan. In 2008, an unknown contributor added a folder of genealogical information on the Ennis, Allen, Hall and Walters families. The collection is arranged by subject.</p>
